(531, '_transient_dash_88ae138922fe95674369b1cb3d215a2b', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/11/wordpress-4-4-beta-3/''>WordPress 4.4 Beta 3</a> <span class="rss-date">November 4, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.4 Beta 3 is now available for download and testing. This is software still in development, so we don’t recommend that you run it on a production site. To get the beta, try the WordPress Beta Tester plugin (you’ll want “bleeding edge nightlies”). Or you can download the beta here (zip). For more of what’s new in version 4.4, check out [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><p><strong>RSS Error</strong>: WP HTTP Error: Operation timed out after 0 milliseconds with 0 out of 0 bytes received</p></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul></ul></div>', 'no'),
